<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-41-1167 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report provides a characterisation of each of the main technologieswhich were included in the 1986 Energy Appraisal, including: 1) extractiontechnologies, 2) electricity production technologies, 3) energy supplytechnologies, 4) energy conversion technologies, 5) energy utilisationtechnologies. It contains detailed modules which provide for each technologya brief technical description and a review of the current status of RDandamp; D programmes primarily in the UK but with some coverage of major overseaseffort.</TEXT></DOC>